n-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他还首次巡演了取自他 1992 年同名专辑的《Lucky Town》，以及收录在《Born In The USA》中的《I&#39;m On Fire》。您可以在下面收听。</p><p>此前，他最近邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">汤姆·莫雷洛（Tom Morello）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bruce-springsteen-enlist-tom-morello-for-two-tour-debuts-3615222">在他正在进行的美国巡演中首次帮助演唱两首歌</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bruce Springsteen &amp; The E Street Band - Lucky Town - 安卡斯维尔，康涅狄格州 - 4.12.24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KME17Um_Oy8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bruce Springsteen &amp; The E Street Band - I&#39;m on Fire- 安卡斯维尔，康涅狄格州 - 4.12.24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ouordBB5qqg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他地方，Boss 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-mark-knopfler-star-studded-going-home-teenage-cancer-trust-3601691">参加了 Mark Knopfler 众星云集的慈善重新录制的《Going Home》</a> ，主演包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a>乐队的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">Brian May</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">Bruce Springsteen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的 Tony Iommi、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>吉他手等。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德</a>等等。</p><p>他还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-cameo-curb-your-enthusiasm-larry-david-3586431">最近一集中客串了《<i>遏制你的热情》</i></a> ，并<a hre